snippet.title: SYNCED: Off-Planet - Cinematic Trailer | Game Awards 2021
snippet.description:
SYNCED: Off-Planet is a companion shooter set in a techno-apocalyptic future. Developed by NEXT Studios and coming to PC in 2022.
